nt (tensions around</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743263-monolithic-power-systems-big-growth-at-a-reasonable-price", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:14:39"}, {"id": "4743262", "title": "Gran Tierra Energy: Links With Trafigura And New Oil Discovery Make It A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil prices and Australian Dollars\" data-id=\"171322198\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1382px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cogal/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Gran Tierra Energy Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GTE\" title=\"Gran Tierra Energy Inc.\">GTE</a></span>) reports links with Trafigura and recently reported a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/19930080-gran-tierra-energy-inc-announces-exploration-success-in-ecuador-and-strategic-joint-venture#hasComeFromMpArticle=false\">new discovery</a> in Ecuador and new <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4339123-gran-tierra-makes-new-oil-discovery-in-ecuador-launches-jv-with-logan-energy\">joint venture agreement</a>. If we also take into account the acquisition of I3</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743262-gran-tierra-energy-links-with-trafigura-and-new-oil-discovery-make-it-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:03:54"}, {"id": "4742937", "title": "Time And Tide Fix The Overvaluation For MEG Energy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil Refinery Aerial Photo\" data-id=\"155159994\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">dan_prat/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong><em>Note: Amounts are in CAD and all prices referenced are on TSX unless stated otherwise.</em></strong></p> <p>Our work on MEG Energy Corp. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MEGEF\" title=\"MEG Energy Corp.\">OTCPK:MEGEF</a>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MEG:CA\" title=\"MEG Energy Corp.\">MEG:CA</a></span>) started off with a buy rating in 2022. At the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742937-time-and-tide-fix-the-overvaluation-for-meg-energy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4743270", "title": "Dovish Hold Sends The Aussie Lower", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Australian money background\" data-id=\"477047608\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">enjoynz</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Overview</h2> <p>The US dollar (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DXY\" title=\"US Dollar Index\">DXY</a></span>) is little changed against most of the G10 currencies today. The Antipodean currencies are the main exception. A modest change in tone from the Reserve Bank of Australia, boosting the chances of a rate cut</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477047608/image_477047608.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743270-dovish-hold-sends-aussie-lower", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 15:50:00"}, {"id": "4743256", "title": "XSOE: One Of The Key Ways To Outperform In Emerging Markets", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"banknotes of the BRICS states\" data-id=\"1733709478\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Bjoern Wylezich</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Opportunity Overview</strong></h2> <p>Emerging markets have had a bumpy ride in the past five years but appear to be in the initial phases of a new bull run. Inflation has improved and economic growth prospects are now stronger in many</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743256-xsoe-one-of-the-key-ways-to-outperform-in-emerging-markets", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 15:44:28"}, {"id": "4743253", "title": "Global Advertising At An All-Time High, But WPP Not A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The renovated Amsteldok building, designed by architect Huig Maaskant, base of multinational advertising and marketing services group WPP\" data-id=\"1802271297\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Milos Ruzicka</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article primarily has the aim, as could be expected on Seeking Alpha, to form an opinion on WPP (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WPPGF\" title=\"WPP plc\">OTCPK:WPPGF</a>) from an investor perspective. There's a secondary aim, though, for people interested in the media sector in general, to touch</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743253-global-advertising-at-an-all-time-high-but-wpp-not-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 15:36:55"}, {"id": "4743252", "title": "DoorDash Through And Through: Maintaining With A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bullet-riddled rooms in Quneitra, Syria\" data-id=\"168260235\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Joel Carillet/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis:</h2> <p>DoorDash (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DASH\" title=\"DoorDash, Inc.\">DASH</a></span>) announced <a href=\"https://ir.doordash.com/news/news-details/2024/DoorDash-Releases-Third-Quarter-2024-Financial-Results/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Q3 earnings</a> in late October, marking its first profitable quarter since the pandemic (and going public), sending shares up 14% since then, well outperforming the S&amp;P 500, up 5.5%. I last wrote on Dash in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743252-doordash-through-and-through-maintaining-with-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 15:35:46"}, {"id": "4743078", "title": "The 2 Worst Mistakes Dividend Investors Keep Making", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A waste paper basket full of red crumpled paper\" data-id=\"1542412718\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542412718/image_1542412718.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury/DigitalVision via Getty